title: DPS-BEST OF- Oct 08, 2020
itunes:title: DPS-BEST OF- Oct 08, 2020
description:
On today's episode of the Dan Patrick Show, DP takes a look at the Titans ongoing Covid outbreak. Will the league force Tennessee to forfeit this weekend's game, after finding out they gathered outside of the team facility? We're joined by TNT's Chris Haynes, MLB HoFer John Smoltz, Reporter covering the Titans Eric Bacharach, and Patriots Insider Tom E. Curran.
